<li>Professor Ashliman of the University of Pittsburg quotes the <a href="http://www.pitt.edu/~dash/hameln.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pitt.edu/~dash/hameln.html" rel="nofollow">Grimm's "Children of Hamelin"</a> in full, as well as a number of similar and related legends.</li>
